00:00:16.020 --> 00:00:19.400
what I usually do is if I know I'm going to travel,

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:19.590
say,

00:00:19.590 --> 00:00:21.890
to Germany or Korea or someplace like that.

00:00:21.890 --> 00:00:25.510
I have a regimen that I put in place now this will depend on the level of my language.

00:00:25.510 --> 00:00:28.940
