00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:17.330
and I try to create a schedule so that by the time I go there,

00:01:17.330 --> 00:01:19.050
everything is pretty much all set.

00:01:19.050 --> 00:01:21.530
I went to Germany recently and that was what I did.

